snippet.title: Legends of IdleOn! -- Idle MMO trailer
snippet.description:
PLAY IDLEON HERE:
Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.lavaflame.MMO&hl=en_US&gl=US
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1476970/Legends_of_IdleOn__Idle_MMO/
iOS: https://apps.apple.com/app/apple-store/id1636526901?pt=120438346&ct=SBaniAd&mt=8

The Idle MMORPG game where you play as dudes with no faces that go door to door scaring kids into eating their vegetables, to great success and applause from the parents! No hang on, that's my other game. This one's just an MMO that plays itself or something like that... 
If you're interested in the 1st game, its called My Nextdoor Neighbors (I had a very traumatic childhood, but at least I eat my veggies!)
